·         Processor: i7 

·         Memory: 16 GB

·         Storage: 256 GB (SSD)

Software Requirements

·         OS: Window/Mac/Linux

·         Browser: Chrome

·         Code Editor:  Visual Studio Code

·         Others: Node JS , npm , Android Studio , XCode and Android SDK, Java 8 
